name: Traditional Maid Dress
description:
weight 0.6-1.0

recommond hires.fix

普通的女仆装词条总是出现露胸装迷你裙的类型,于是由于XP试着炼了一个比较传统保守的女仆装,

三次元二次元皆可使用,建议大胸使用较高权重,但还是有可能出现露胸装,多试几次吧

Simple maid prompt always show topless clothes and miniskirt, so I tried to make a more traditional and conservative maid dress,

Both real and anim can be used. Recommended to use a higher weight for large breasts, but still show topless clothes sometimes. Try a few more times.
